# TaskFlow — API and security

- JWT secret from `.env` only (`JWT_SECRET`); never hardcode; reject default `change-me` when `APP_ENV=prod`.
- Validate every input (length, format, type) before use; use `ValidationService` patterns.
- JSON shape: `{ success, data, error, meta }` via `ResponseService`.
- CORS: explicit origin (`CORS_ALLOW_ORIGIN`); no `*` in production with credentials.
- Rate limit: ~60 req/min per IP (file bucket or Redis); see `RateLimitMiddleware`.
- HTML output from PHP: escape with `htmlspecialchars` / context-appropriate escaping.
